# SkillUp â€“ Online Learning & Assessment Platform

## Overview
SkillUp is a web-based EduTech platform designed to provide structured online learning and assessment for students and educators.  
It allows students to access courses, take quizzes, track progress, while educators can upload lessons, manage learners, and issue certificates.

## Features
- Student & Educator registration/login
- Course listing and enrollment
- Interactive lessons and quizzes
- Automated grading system
- Student dashboard to track progress
- Admin panel for educators

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React.js  
- **Backend:** Node.js / Express  
- **Database:** MongoDB or PostgreSQL  
- **Authentication:** JWT (JSON Web Tokens)  
- **Deployment:** Netlify (frontend), Heroku (backend)

